      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "It occurred to me that this year could be last time that the old Bernabéu shows up in a new video game... so I went to sleep last night <em>unhingedly</em> imagining some sort of tribute to the Real Madrid players that became icons in my career saves—ever since becoming addicted to manager modes with <em>PES 4</em> and <em>FIFA 2004</em>."
